{"title":"时间开始了！","authors":["胡风"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":11,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"时间开始了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胡风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一乐章：欢乐颂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时间开始了——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他站到了主席台底正中间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他站在飘着四面红旗的地球面底"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国地形正前面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他屹立着象一尊塑像……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掌声和呼声静下来了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这会场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"静下来了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好象是风浪停息了的海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有微波在动荡而过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有微风在吹拂而过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一刹那通到永远——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔腾在肃穆的呼吸里面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨过了这肃穆的一刹那"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时间！时间！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你一跃地站了起来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东，他向世界发出了声音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东，他向时间发出了命令"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“进军！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掌声爆发了起来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乐声奔涌了出来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灯光放射了开来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"礼炮象大交响乐的鼓声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“咚！咚！咚！”地轰响了进来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这会场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一瞬间化成了一片沸腾的海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片声浪的海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片光带的海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片声浪和光带交错着的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢跃的生命的海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沸腾着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它涌着一个最高峰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他屹然地站在那最高峰上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好象他微微俯着身躯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好象他右手握紧拳头放在前面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好象他双脚踩着一个"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巨大的无形的舵盘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好象他在凝视着流到了这里的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各种各样的河流"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他屹然地站在那最高峰上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好象他在向着自己"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也就是向着全世界宣布："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让带着泥沙的流到这里来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让浮着血污的流到这里来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让沾着尸臭的流到这里来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让千千万万的清流流到这里来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也让千千万万的浊流流到这里来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"…………………………………"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要大"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大到能够"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"环抱世界"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大到能够"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流贯永远"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要容纳应该容纳的一切"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能澄清应该澄清的一切"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我这晶莹无际的碧蓝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要用它纯洁的幸福光波"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"映照在这个大宇宙中间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海在沸腾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他屹然地站在那最高峰上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那不是挥动巨掌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"击落着无数飞箭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而奔驰前进的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火焰似的列宁底姿势"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那不是斩掉了一切毒瘤以后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重量和力量的凝合体"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泰山石敢当的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢柱似的斯大林底姿势"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"列宁、斯大林底这个伟大的学生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他微微俯着身躯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好象正要迈开大步的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"神话里的巨人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在紧张地估计着前面的方向"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"握得紧紧的右手的拳头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抓住了无数的中国河流"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他劝告它们跟着他前进"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他命令它们跟着他前进"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗人但丁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当年在地狱门上写下了一句金言："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“到这里来的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切希望都要放弃！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国人民底诗人毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在中国新生的时间大门上面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写下了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但丁没有幸运写下的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使人感到幸福"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而不是感到痛苦的句子："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“一切愿意新生的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到这里来罢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最美好最纯洁的希望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在等待着你！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的祖国呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在你忍受灾难的怀抱里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我所分得的微小的屈辱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和微小的悲痛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也是永世难忘的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但终于到了今天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了你的新生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我奉上这欢喜的泪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了你的母爱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我奉上这感激的泪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国，我的祖国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在你新生的这神圣的时间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全地球都在向你敬礼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全宇宙都在向你祝贺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷声响起了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轰轰轰地在你头上滚动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨点打来了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花花花地在你头上飘舞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全宇宙都在欢唱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这大自然底交响乐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那么雄伟又那么慈和"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘流在这一片生命的海上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我感到了你巨大的心房"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在激烈地鼓动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦幻的我的眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝向了右边一瞥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看见了一个老人底侧脸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的头发象一蓬秋草"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的胡子钢一样翘着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"激动得张开着的嘴巴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忘记了动作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我感到了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的额头上在冒着热汗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我感到了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我看不到的他的眼睛里面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在燃烧着火焰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的战友"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的兄弟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看见了你！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你在臭湿的牢房垂死过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你在荒野的乡村冻饿过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你和穷苦的农民一道喂过虱子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你和勇敢的战友一道喝过血水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你受过了千锤百炼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你征服了痛苦和死亡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这中间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少年多少年了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但你的希望活到了今天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的意志活到了今天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"激动着你的此刻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你忘记了过去的一切罢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但过去的一切"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使你纯真得象一个婴儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛躺在温暖的摇篮里面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洁白的心房充溢着新生的恩惠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你也感到了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这摇撼着雷雨的大交响底抚慰罢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是催生歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也是催眠曲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我梦幻的心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荡漾着一片醉意"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越过你的侧脸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘忽地回到了七月一日的狂风暴雨下面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好猛烈的狂风暴雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好甜蜜的狂风暴雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夹着雷声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞着电火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倾天覆地而来了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被你吹着淋着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是三万个战斗的生命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用歌声迎接你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用欢笑迎接你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用舞蹈迎接你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有你这响彻天地的大合奏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有你这湿透发肤的大洗礼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才能满足这神圣的生日所怀抱的大"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢喜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"圆形的大会场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象一个浮在大宇宙中间的地球"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整列在那边缘上的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湿透了的无数红旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘舞得更响更欢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好象在歌唱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘舞得更红更鲜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好象是跳跃着的火焰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被它们照临着的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三万颗战斗的心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被暴雨洗过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被狂风吹着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也更响更欢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也更红更鲜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"突然"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个克服了艰险的历程"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走到了胜利的战列前行的钢人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中断了他的发言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用着只有那么镇定"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才能表现他所感到的光荣的声音宣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"布了："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——我们的毛主席来到！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三万个激动的声音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢呼了起来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好象是从地面飞起的暴雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三万个激动的面孔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"转向了一边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好象是被大旋风吹向着一点"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三万个激动的心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拥抱着融合着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汇成了掀播着的不能分割的海面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"圆形海面的边缘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整列着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湿透了的无数红旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘舞得更响更欢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好象在歌唱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘舞得更红更鲜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好象是跳跃着的火焰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它们歌唱着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝向一点"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它们跳跃着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝向一点"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三万个战斗的生命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一个都在心里告诉自己："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——毛主席，毛主席，他在这"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"里！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——毛主席，毛主席，他和我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在一起！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他在这里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在他正对着的那一边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矗立着四幅巨像"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——马克思、恩格斯、列宁、斯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动人类底四颗伟大的心脏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人类福音底四面神圣的旗子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四幅巨像"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前面放射着灯光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正对着他们天才的学生毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和三万个战斗的生命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所汇成的海面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四幅巨像"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"背后是无际的天空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑沉沉的远方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷声还在隐隐地滚动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电火还在一闪一闪地飞现"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四幅巨像"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被这大自然底交响乐伴奏着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使我们和大宇宙年青的生命融合在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使我们和全地球未完的战斗连结在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一刹那通到无际……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一刹那通到无际——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他站在这里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轰轰的雷声在滚动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花花的雨声在歌唱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掀播着这声浪和光带交错着的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又一个生命的海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掀播着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涌着一个最高峰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他屹然地站在那里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他背后的地球形上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照临着碧蓝的天空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦幻的我的眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又看见了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那四幅巨像"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矗立着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"若隐若现"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那碧蓝的亮光中间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好象飞来了雷声底隐隐滚动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好象射来了电火底一闪一闪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东！毛泽东！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"由于你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的祖国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的人民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感到了太空底永生的呼吸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"受到了全地球本身底战斗的召唤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你屹然地站在最高峰上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你感到了那个呼吸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你听到了那个召唤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你微微俯着身躯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你坚定地望着前面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是那个唯一的方向"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是无数河流汇合之点"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你两脚踩着无形的巨大的舵盘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你坚定地望着望着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那上面闪现过了什么呢？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪现过了一个面影："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赤裸着身子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被绑着送向法场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在英勇地喊着口号吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪现过了一个面影："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被装在麻袋里面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抛到了河里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"传来了一声水响吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪现过了一个面影："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双脚被捆了起来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"由烈马倒拖着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔驰而过吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪现过了一个面影："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在草地里陷了下去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿童的脑袋沉没了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双手还在抓扑吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪现过了一个面影："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在雪山边坐了下来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即刻僵冻住了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"定在那里永远不动吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪现过了一个面影："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了不让敌人发现"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用母亲的战栗的手扣住幼儿底咽喉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望着他僵冷下去了吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪现过了一个面影："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抱着炸药包"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲到碉堡底下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让身体和它同时粉碎了吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪现过了一个面影："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把飞舞的红旗插上了敌人阵地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身里的热血同时喷了出来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在旗杆旁边倒下了吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗挂在电线柱子上的头颅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪现过了吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一具倒毙在暗牢里的尸体"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪现过了吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个埋进土里的半截身子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪现过了吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"…………………"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"…………………"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的战友"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的兄弟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的同志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艰险的时候想到你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忍苦的时候想到你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"受刑的时候想到你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"献命的时候想到你……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在祖国新生的温暖怀抱里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们复活了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏着雄壮的步子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现出欢喜的笑容"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亮着温爱的目光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举起健康的手臂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蜂群似地来了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪潮似地来了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来了来了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来向你欢呼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来向你致敬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来向你祝贺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东！毛泽东！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国第一个光荣的布尔塞维克"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们的力量"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汇集着活在你的身上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你抓住了无数的河流"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们的意志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汇集着活在你的心里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你挑起了这一部历史"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东！毛泽东！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国大地最无畏的战士"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国人民最亲爱的儿子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你微微俯着巨人的身躯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你坚定地望着前面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随着你抬起的手势"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大自然底交响乐涌出了最高音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全人类底大希望发出了最强光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你镇定地迈开了第一步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你沉着的声音象一响惊雷——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“全人类四分之一的中国人从此站立"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起来了！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——一九四九、十一月十一日夜十时半，成。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十一月十二日夜十一时，改。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在北京。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}